  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (M&E)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities and Duties</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assisting Project Manager</li>\n  <li>Preparing Tender and contract documents</li>\n  <li>Handle the negotiation rates and quotations from sub contractors</li>\n  <li>Collate information and present for tender submission</li>\n  <li>Liasing with clients, consultants and contractors</li>\n  <li>Site viewing and understanding</li>\n  <li>All other necessary admin works related to work scope</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications and Skills</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma / Degree in Civil/Building/Architecture Engineering or any relevant discipline</li>\n  <li>3-5 years of experience in civil / construction industry</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under pressure and tight schedules to meet tendering submission deadlines</li>\n  <li>Good communication, writing &amp; interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in building standards, measurement, documentation and contractual issues</li>\n</ul>",
